summary: This is an email from the U.S. Attorney's Office for the Southern District of New York (USAO SDNY) forwarding a voice message attachment from an unidentified caller. The email is addressed to the Epstein Victims notification list and includes a timestamp indicating the message was recorded on August 14, 2019.

events.title: Voice Message Received by USAO SDNY
events.description: A voice message was recorded and forwarded by the U.S. Attorney's Office for the Southern District of New York to the Epstein Victims notification list.

keyFacts: The U.S. Attorney's Office for the Southern District of New York (USAO SDNY) received a voice message on August 14, 2019.
The voice message was forwarded via email to the 'USANYS-EpsteinVictims' distribution list.
The email includes an audio file attachment named '0190814 082835.wav' containing the voice message.
